Attn: User Support, DMCA complaints

1. The copyrighted work at issue consists of text (content) and images that appear in their original form on www.incensegalore.com and that have beeen reproduced without  consent or permission on www.flamingincense.com.

2.	Search Query:	"and you'll enjoy the lingering aroma" (within quotes)
Infringing Web Pages:	www.flamingincense.com/

Additional stolen content and images can be located throughout the flamingincense site.

3.	I can be contacted by telephone at 208 [private] or by e-mail at [private]@incensegalore.com.

4.	The e-mail address for flamingincense.com is posted as [private]@sbcglobal.net.

5.	"I have a good faith belief that use of the copyrighted materials described above on the allegedly infringing web pages is not authorized by the copyright owner, its agent, or the law."

6.	"I swear, under penalty of perjury, that the information in the notification is accurate and that I am the copyright owner or am authorized to act on behalf of the owner of an exclusive right that is allegedly infringed."

7.	Signature.

8.	Send the written communication to the following address:

Google, Inc.
Attn: User Support, DMCA Complaints [private]
Mountain View, CA 94043
OR fax to:
